ecomposition of circulant matrices within the code\ndiversity framework. A 3 by 3 circulant code is shown to outperform the\nAlamouti code at the same transmission rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Sep 2008 05:30:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
